7
00:00:30,759 --> 00:00:37,309
First, will there be crowding out? By definition,
crowding out is the decrease in private expenditures

8
00:00:37,309 --> 00:00:41,440
that occurs as a consequence of increased
government spending, or the financing needs

9
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:47,640
